<subSubSection id="EBEABDD9FF86FFFA39D30C0C4695B327" pageId="8" pageNumber="235" type="description">
<paragraph id="A34FEE52FF86FFFA39D30C0C4695B327" blockId="8.[136,1452,1850,2057]" pageId="8" pageNumber="235">
<emphasis id="91843240FF86FFFA39D30C0C4626BC7B" bold="true" box="[136,264,1850,1876]" pageId="8" pageNumber="235">Subshrubs</emphasis>
<quantity id="640843B7FF86FFFA38540C0C4650BC7A" box="[271,382,1850,1877]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.5" metricValueMax="8.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="235" unit="cm" value="65.0" valueMax="80.0" valueMin="50.0">50–80 cm</quantity>
tall, usually cespitose, bearing a well-developed, woody underground root-like system. 
<emphasis id="91843240FF86FFFA3C020C0C4285BC7B" bold="true" box="[1369,1451,1850,1876]" pageId="8" pageNumber="235">Leaves</emphasis>
with 8–11 pairs of pinnae; 10–15(–18) pairs of leaflets; rachis nectaries 2–4, verruciform; blade chartaceous, margin ciliate, leaflets (6–)10–15 × (2–) 
<quantity id="640843B7FF86FFFA38A90CB4457CBCB2" box="[498,594,1922,1949]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" metricValueMax="8.0" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="235" unit="mm" value="6.0" valueMax="8.0" valueMin="4.0">4–8 mm</quantity>
, discolor, glabrous on both surfaces, with sparse trichomes along the midrib, unilateral tuft of trichomes on the lower surface absent. 
<emphasis id="91843240FF86FFFA3A5C0C90449EBCEF" bold="true" box="[775,944,1958,1984]" pageId="8" pageNumber="235">Inflorescences</emphasis>
of simple thyrsi; cymulae of solitary spikes, vinaceous. 
<emphasis id="91843240FF86FFFA385C0CFC4648BCCB" bold="true" box="[263,358,1994,2020]" pageId="8" pageNumber="235">Flowers</emphasis>
monoclinous, purplish to rarely pinkish. 
<emphasis id="91843240FF86FFFA3A620CFC4459BCCB" bold="true" box="[825,887,1994,2020]" pageId="8" pageNumber="235">Fruit</emphasis>
a follicule, straight, flat-compressed, 5.5–8 × 
<quantity id="640843B7FF86FFFA3C210CFC47F9B326" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2999999999999998" metricValueMax="1.4" metricValueMin="1.2" pageId="8" pageNumber="235" unit="cm" value="1.2999999999999998" valueMax="1.4" valueMin="1.2">1.2– 1.4 cm</quantity>
, valves dark-brown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
